{
  "texts": [
    "However, exploratory research needs to be conducted specifically in the context of social media and how the user responds to explainable recommendations.",
    "However, the lack of end usercentric studies also adds to the urgency of investigating social media recommendations from an exploratory point of view.",
    "Our research aimed to explore the user perception of explainable social media recommendations that fall under the umbrella of explainable AI.",
    "In this work, we have collected qualitative data using semi-structured interviews.",
    "Qualitative research is used across various disciplines, traditionally in the social sciences but also nowadays in human-computer interaction, which requires human insights."
  ]
}